{
  "stem": "12053.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only thing I specified, you have to state your name, former name, town of origin, and town of domicile now, above your story.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise I won't accept it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To show it's a historical book and that we really existed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the letters came pouring in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also before them, the thing that really most reunited people and still reunites them today, is my wonderful brochure.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A friend of ours, late-- he became, also, my co-editor-- wonderful person, Shmuel Lowensohn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He compiled this most wonderful, wonderful brochure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And why is it so wonderful?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it contains the names, former names, towns of origin, and all the addresses of hundreds and hundreds of people, participants and nonparticipants at the reunion from all over the world.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody went home with their brochure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And other people who contributed-- it was very, very expensive to produce because of so much write-- written matter in it with tiny little printed names.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It went around the world.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It still goes around the world.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the usual thing, when you have a brochure, you throw it out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this brochure, I don't think anybody ever threw one of those brochures away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people are writing to each other, and friends of friends of friends, they're getting to know each other.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, people don't understand-- if you have families, if you grow up in a normal way, you have lots of families-- cousins, and cousins, and aunts, and uncles, and second cousins.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't bother with all of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if you're on your own in a str-- you know, came as a refugee, you haven't got any relatives, to find somebody who once knew your parents, to find an old school friend, it's a tremendous thing.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is something that people do not realize.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
